Build a modern, responsive web application called "Proposal Generator" for an Event Production Company.

Purpose:
The application should allow sales teams to quickly create professional client proposals by selecting materials from an uploaded master list instead of manually typing everything.

Technology:
- React (Next.js preferred)
- Node.js + Express (or Next.js API routes)
- SQLite or Supabase for storage
- Tailwind CSS
- Clean modern UI
- Mobile responsive

